Developer Terms of Use
des:
Startup Assistant determines what stage your startup is at and gives you custom advice at each stage. Whether you are at the concept stage or scaling stage, this skill allows you to conveniently receive advice curated towards the specific stage your startup is in.

IS STARTUP ASSISTANT FREE?
Yes! Anyone can enable Startup Assistant, and get custom tips and strategies to elevate your business along the way at each stage.

FEEDBACK
We hope you find Startup Assistant to be a delightful experience. If you have feedback or suggestions on how to make the skill more enjoyable, please contact us at danielharris053@gmail.com.
